dock where it automatically empties the dustbin and washes the mop pads using 80 degree hot water. It even achieves a 99.9% bacterial removal rate, so it's always clean, fresh, and ready for the next mess. And honestly, anything that helps me spend less time cleaning and more time relaxing is a win in my books."}]}